  "body": "How will MEV-boost handle auth for CL<>EL communication? https://github.com/ethereum/execution-apis/blob/main/src/engine/authentication.md \r\n\r\nSeems like most requests could just be forwarded, but `engine_forkchoiceUpdatedV1` will need to be sent to the relay. So I think MEV-boost will need to accept a `jwt-secret` to let it decrypt `engine_forkchoiceUpdatedV1` before sending it to the relay.",
